high_descs: Adjust yourself slightly to stand and face the middle of the sink.
Open the left side cabinet door under the sink and get the black cloth from under there before closing the door again.
Walk over to the tub so you are facing the left side of it.
Place the cloth in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place a cloth in the tub.

high_descs: Go to the sink behind you.
Go to the left cabinet beneath the sink and take out the cloth.
Go to the bath tub to your left.
Put the cloth in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Place a cloth in a bath tub.

high_descs: Turn around and face the sink.
Open the left door of the cabinet below the sink to take out a black towel.
Turn left and walk towards the bath tub.
Place the towel in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Take the towel from the cabinet to put it in the tub.
